										<li id="comment-90437" class="commentbody"><div class="commenthead"><img alt='Martin Hay`s avatar' src='http://trilema.com/default_avatar.png' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' />								<div class="commentcount">43</div>
