<p><a href="http://wiki.bitcoin-otc.com/wiki/GPG_Contract">http://wiki.bitcoin-otc.com/wiki/GPG_Contract</a></p>
<p>What makes a GPG contract unenforceable?  What is it that gives a party the safety and knowledge that it can be enforced against them?</p>
